OL,6,FThe British Medical Association (BMA)
OL,7,Fhas also joined legal action being
OL,8,Fbrought against the medical regulator,
OL,9,Fas revealed exclusively by ITV News in
OL,10,FOctober.
OL,12,FThey are joining a legal case against
OL,13,Fthe GMC alongside the campaign group
OL,14,FAnaesthetists United. The BMA will
OL,15,Ffinancially support the case.
