OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThe academy called for an
OL,12,Finvestigation into whether using
OL,13,Fmedical associates was safe, cost-
OL,14,Feffective and efficient.
OL,16,FThe government has now announced a
OL,17,Freview will take place, led by
OL,18,FProfessor Gillian Leng, who is
OL,19,Fpresident of the Royal Society of
OL,20,FMedicine.
