OL,6,FThe review is due to report in the
OL,7,Fspring and will include
OL,8,Frecommendations on how the roles
OL,9,Fshould work in the future, as part of
OL,10,Fthe government's 10-year plan for the
OL,11,FNHS.
OL,13,FStreeting said many physician
OL,14,Fassociates "are providing great care"
OL,15,Fand "freeing up doctors to do the
OL,16,Fthings only doctors can do".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
