OL,4,Cphysician associates in the NHS
OL,6,F"But there are legitimate concerns
OL,7,Fover transparency for patients, scope
OL,8,Fof practice, and the substituting of
OL,9,Fdoctors. These concerns have been
OL,10,Fignored for too long, leading to a
OL,11,Ftoxic debate where physicians feel
OL,12,Fignored and PAs feel demoralised.
OL,14,FHe added that the independent review
OL,15,Fwould "establish the facts, take the
OL,16,Fheat out of the issue, and make sure
OL,17,Fthat we get the right people, in the
OL,18,Fright place, doing the right thing".
OL,20,FThe GMC will begin regulating PA and
OL,21,FAAs from December.
