OL,6,FIn a statement it said: "Regulation is
OL,7,Fa vital step towards strengthening
OL,8,Fboth patient safety and public trust
OL,9,Fin these professions. It will help
OL,10,Fprovide assurance to patients,
OL,11,Femployers and colleagues that PAs and
OL,12,FAAs have the right level of education
OL,13,Fand training, meet the standards that
OL,14,Fwe expect of the professions we
OL,15,Fregulate and that they can be held to
OL,16,Faccount if serious concerns are
OL,17,Fraised."
OL,19,F"We have patient safety concerns raise
OL,20,Fwith us by our members on almost a
OL,21,Fdaily basis."
