OL,6,FBut the BMA is calling for immediate
OL,7,Fsafety measures.
OL,9,F"You do not fly a plane under safety
OL,10,Freview, you ground it," the
OL,11,Fassociation's council chair Professor
OL,12,FPhil Banfield said.
OL,14,F"So we need to know what immediate
OL,15,Fsafety measures NHS England will put
OL,16,Fin place, how quickly they will pause
OL,17,Ftheir PA expansion plans, and in the
OL,18,Fmeantime if they will adopt the BMA's
OL,19,Fown guidelines to start protecting
OL,20,Fpatients now.
OL,26,@qD@AOU
