OL,6,FBut NHS England insists physician
OL,7,Fassociates and anaesthesia associates
OL,8,Fare "important members of NHS staff".
OL,10,FAmanda Pritchard, chief executive of
OL,11,FNHS England, said: "They come to work
OL,12,Fevery day to help care for patients
OL,13,Fand so they deserve to be treated with
OL,14,Fthe same respect as anyone else coming
OL,15,Fto work in the NHS.
